<section id="provenance_ref">
  <title>ref</title>

  <para>Reference - holds a reference to the element the enclosing <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/provenance/provenance.xml" targetptr="provenance_element"
        ><code>&lt;provenance&gt;</code></olink> element applies to.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis> A value of type anyURI. When used in a <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/provenance/provenance.xml" targetptr="provenance_element"
        ><code>&lt;provenance&gt;</code></olink> element, the URI value refers to a specific <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"
        ><code>&lt;unit&gt;</code></olink> element.</para>

  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined</para>

  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis> <olink targetdoc="../../elements/provenance/provenance.xml"
      targetptr="provenance_element"><code>&lt;provenance&gt;</code></olink>.</para>
</section>
